configurationRules.configuration:
{
	"query":"SELECT * FROM ios_product.users WHERE ups_id IN (%s)",
	"multiTablesQuery":"SELECT BASIC.*,  PI.*, (select array_agg(PP.*) from (ios_product.purchases_users inner join ios_product.purchases on ios_product.purchases.id = ios_product.purchases_users.purchase_id) as PP where PP.user_id = BASIC.id) as PURCHASES_ARRAY FROM ((ios_product.users as BASIC left join ios_product.users_pi as PI ON BASIC.id = PI.id)) WHERE PI.ups_id IN (%s)",
	"multiTablesQuery_dev":"SELECT BASIC.*,  PI.*, (select array_agg(PP.*) from (ios_product_dev.purchases_users inner join ios_product_dev.purchases on ios_product_dev.purchases.id = ios_product_dev.purchases_users.purchase_id) as PP where PP.user_id = BASIC.id) as PURCHASES_ARRAY FROM ((ios_product_dev.users as BASIC left join ios_product_dev.users_pi as PI ON BASIC.id = PI.id)) WHERE PI.ups_id IN (%s)",
	"usersForDelete":"SELECT BASIC.id, BASIC.shard, BASIC.first_session, PI.ups_id FROM ((ios_product.users as BASIC left join ios_product.users_pi as PI ON BASIC.id = PI.id)) WHERE PI.ups_id IN (%s)",
	"usersForDelete_dev":"SELECT BASIC.id, BASIC.shard, BASIC.first_session, PI.ups_id FROM ((ios_product_dev.users as BASIC left join ios_product_dev.users_pi as PI ON BASIC.id = PI.id)) WHERE PI.ups_id IN (%s)"
}
